"560"/></picture></div><figcaption class="Slideshow-caption"><p class="Slideshow-imageText">Johan Kreicbergs, företagarekonom på Svenskt näringsliv, räds att många jobb kommer att gå förlorade om regeringen inte förlänger omsättningsstödet till företag.    </p><span class="Slideshow-imageByline"> Foto: Privat</span></figcaption><i class="FontIcon FontIcon--large FontIcon--circled-arrow-up Slideshow-caption-icon"></i></figure></div></div><div class="js-overlay-slideshow-trigger"></div><div class="Slideshow-navigatePrevNext"><button type="button" class="Slideshow-navigate Slideshow-navigate--prev FontIcon FontIcon--arrow-left js-slideshow-prev" aria-label="Föregående"></button><button type="button" class="Slideshow-navigate Slideshow-navigate--next FontIcon FontIcon--arrow-right js-slideshow-next" aria-label="Nästa"></button></div></div></div><div class="Container Container--ad Container--ad-panorama AdOuterMostContainer u-noPrint"><div id="AdWrapper-id-position-id--bd8ab6ca-d8ed-41ef-b779-9d37e434585f--naringsliv-article--top-1" class=" AdWrapper"><div id="Ad-id-position-id--bd8ab6ca-d8ed-41ef-b779-9d37e434585f--naringsliv-article--top-1" class="Ad Ad--panorama  Ad--unused" data-controller="postMessage" data-postmessage-command="hideAd,parallax-mobile,resizeAd,resizeMediationAd,toggleDarkmode,decorateSpinner" data-postmessage-origins="*"><div class="Ad-text">Annons</div><div id="AdWrapperInner-id-position-id--bd8ab6ca-d8ed-41ef-b779-9d37e434585f--naringsliv-article--top-1" class="Ad-content AdWrapper-inner" style="min-height:240px"><div id="AdPosition-container-wrapper-id-position-id--bd8ab6ca-d8ed-41ef-b779-9d37e434585f--naringsliv-article--top-1" class="AdPosition" data-svd-ad-position-id="position-id--bd8ab6ca-d8ed-41ef-b779-9d37e434585f--naringsliv-article--top-1" data-svd-ad-position-type="top" data-svd-ad-position-handled-height="false"><div id="AdPosition-container-id-position-id--bd8ab6ca-d8ed-41ef-b779-9d37e434585f--naringsliv-article--top-1" class="AdPositi